==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Waterwort
<hw>Wa"ter*wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of the natural order <ord>Elatineae</ord>, consisting of
two genera (<gen>Elatine</gen>, and <gen>Bergia</gen>), mostly small
annual herbs growing in the edges of ponds. Some have a peppery or acrid
taste.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Watery</ent>⟦br⟧
